title: Joe Lovano on Wayne Shorter
description: Saxophonist Joe Lovano talks about creating a band inspired by the music of Wayne Shorter. This In Person with JazzTimes interview took place backstage inside Fort Adams at the 2012 Newport Jazz Festival, where Lovano performed with Soundprints, the group he co-leads with Dave Douglas. Interview by Lee Mergner. Video by Melissa Mergner. Audio by Jen Kim. Special thanks to Carolyn McClair, Melanie Nanez, Dan Melnick, Deborah Ross and the staff of George Wein Productions.
